        <mxCell id="callout" value="This first code sample stops at the view pattern. It does not yet add an automation or outbox translation because the slice only needs a write-side fact and a reviewer-facing query.&#xa;If a later slice auto-approves applications or publishes notifications, add Event -&gt; View -&gt; Automated Trigger -&gt; Command -&gt; Event or translation lanes on a separate board." style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;arcSize=10;fillColor=#FFFFFF;strokeColor=#CBD5E1;strokeWidth=2;fontSize=16;fontColor=#334155;align=left;verticalAlign=middle;spacingLeft=16;spacingRight=16;" vertex="1" parent="1">
